Package org.bonitasoft.engine.bpm.process

Interface ProcessDeploymentInfo

All Superinterfaces:
BaseElement, BonitaObject, DescriptionElement, NamedElement, Serializable
All Known Implementing Classes:
ProcessDeploymentInfoImpl
public interface ProcessDeploymentInfo extends DescriptionElement, BaseElement
Gives access to the ProcessDefinition deployment information.
A ProcessDeploymentInfo has a ConfigurationState, which says if the process is resolved (all its basic configuration has a proper value), or unresolved (some configuration has to be done before the process can be activated).

A ProcessDeploymentInfo has an ActivationState, which says if the process was set to enabled (logged users can start instances of this process), or disabled (no start can be performed on the process).

Author:
Baptiste Mesta, Yanyan Liu, Hongwen Zang, Celine Souchet, Emmanuel Duchastenier
